for X, x being set st x in X holds 
 {x} is Subset of X

label: FUNCT_2:5
query:
for X, Y being set 
 for x being object 
 for f being Function of X,Y st Y <> {} & x in X holds 
 f . x in Y;

label: NAT_1:52
query:
for Y being set 
 for X being non empty set 
 for s being sequence of X st ( for n being Nat holds s . n in Y ) holds 
 rng s c= Y;

label: FINSEQ_2:28
query:
for i being natural Number 
 for D being non empty set 
 for q being FinSequence 
 for f being sequence of D st q = f | (Seg i) holds 
 len q = i;

label: GROUP_19:45
query:
for G being Group 
 for H being Subgroup of G 
 for a being FinSequence of G 
 for b being FinSequence of H st a = b holds 
 Product a = Product b;
